Croatia, another Mediterranean

The crossroads of civilizations since antiquity, Croatia fascinates with its Slavic and Mediterranean flair. Nicknamed "the pearl of the Mediterranean", it sways to the rhythm of the Mediterranean. Tourists there have chosen well, with the Dalmatian coast tracing a winding path hiding a host of treasures.
